      "body": "This bug doesn't do much other than leaving stale entries in `m_block_unlinked`. I think the fix could just be to gate on `BLOCK_HAVE_DATA` before inserting [here](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/58dccd27e11de68f810145fc30631a2c446f3bf5/src/node/blockstorage.cpp#L484).",
